                                 TERRAIN
                                 =======

Terrain is a REQUIRED setting for all rooms. Every room MUST:

    #include <terrain.h>
    
and

    set_terrain(<terrain bit field>);

as part of the room settings. Terrain settings MUST be ORed bit field
settings defined in terrain.h. For example:

    set_terrain(TER_OUTSIDE|TER_PATH|TER_FOREST);

Don't even THINK about using string values like:

    set_terrain("path");

Every room MUST set ALL applicable terrain types. That means that for a
path in the forest,

    set_terrain(TER_PATH|TER_FOREST);

is WRONG because it doesn't have TER_OUTSIDE.

See /open/INCLUDE/terrain.h for currently available terrain settings.

